Write the constructor method in the Intersection class.
Remember to respond with a snippet in the form of the following:
```
class Intersection {
    constructor(curveIndexA, curveIndexB, surfaceIndexA, surfaceIndexB, uParamA, vParamA, uParamB, vParamB, point) {
        // your code here
    }
}
```

```javascript
class Intersection {
    constructor(curveIndexA, curveIndexB, surfaceIndexA, surfaceIndexB, uParamA, vParamA, uParamB, vParamB, point) {
        this.curveIndexA = curveIndexA;
        this.curveIndexB = curveIndexB;
        this.surfaceIndexA = surfaceIndexA;
        this.surfaceIndexB = surfaceIndexB;
        this.uParamA = uParamA;
        this.vParamA = vParamA;
        this.uParamB = uParamB;
        this.vParamB = vParamB;
        this.point = point;
    }
}
```
